Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Great Pirate Era
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.93,0:02:37.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,is experiencing a groundswell\Nbeyond the World Government's expectation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.46,0:02:45.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Being at the center of the unstoppable swell\Nand drawing the most attention is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.94,0:02:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Monkey D. Luffy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.70,0:02:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And the Straw Hats!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.29,0:02:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order to cope with the \Nturbulent Great Pirate Era,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.17,0:03:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}50 leaders hold the World Conference\Nevery four years.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.09,0:03:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Known as the Reverie, it is about to start.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.35,0:03:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The times are changing drastically now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.11,0:03:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"One Step Forward for Her Dream!\NShirahoshi Goes Out in the Sun!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.59,0:03:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How beautiful she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.97,0:03:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire! More than I imagined...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.39,0:04:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we do a feature story on her,\NPresident Morgans?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.03,0:04:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.86,0:04:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,President Morgans?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.57,0:04:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! He's totally captivated by her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.95,0:04:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mermaid Princess-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.12,0:04:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garp, Shirahoshi is very popular-{\i1}jamon{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.37,0:04:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even on land, word is spreading that\NThe Fish-Man Island's Mermaid Princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.84,0:04:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is as beautiful as\NPirate Empress Hancock!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.74,0:04:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so pretty. I'm sure she surpasses\Neveryone's expectations!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.39,0:04:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.44,0:04:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Luffy-{\i1}sama{\i0}'s grandfather-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.10,0:04:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what they call a forest on land?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.20,0:04:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's a tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.78,0:05:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Garp the hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.50,0:05:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know who I am, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.00,0:05:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you stupid brat! Get out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.13,0:05:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Stupid brat"?! I must've heard wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.22,0:05:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Stelly!\NMaybe that's not not-it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.50,0:05:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Stelly, king of the Goa \NKingdom where you come from!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.45,0:05:23.32,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,KING STELLY OF THE GOA KINGDOM IN THE EAST BLUE\N(SABO'S ADOPTED BROTHER)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:28.30,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,And since you're a citizen, \Nyou're one of my subjects!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.32,0:05:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.82,0:05:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm correct, Stelly is your \Nadopted brother, right, Sabo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.37,0:05:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stelly was adopted by Sabo's noble parents.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.13,0:05:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With that as his first foothold,\Nhe looked enviously to connect with royalty{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.38,0:05:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and married Princess Isntoinette.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.09,0:05:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Later, the king and prince of the Goa Kingdom\Nmysteriously died{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.76,0:06:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and several months ago, \NStelly became the king.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.69,0:06:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Goa Kingdom...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.09,0:06:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Gray Terminal in that country is\Nthe place we first met, right, Luffy?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.09,0:06:17.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,GOA KINGDOM
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:22.56,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,GRAY TERMINAL
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.58,0:06:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At once!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.21,0:06:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! You got a lot!\NWay more than I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lot of money!\NHow'd you get that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.92,0:06:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I robbed some thugs near the main gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.97,0:06:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! You won again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.43,0:06:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter if you win or lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.14,0:06:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been five years since we started\Nto put money in our "pirate savings."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.77,0:06:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how much we need\Nto get a pirate ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.29,0:06:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.\N10 million or 100 million maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.05,0:06:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.53,0:06:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A pirate ship"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.45,0:07:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys! Are you gonna become pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.54,0:07:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become one, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.95,0:07:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.25,0:07:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At first, Ace and I didn't accept him,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.09,0:07:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but later, we got close enough to\Nexchange a cup of {\i0}sake{\i1} to become brothers.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.47,0:07:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So from now on,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.07,0:07:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we're brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.64,0:07:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.69,0:07:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ace, Luffy and I did as we liked{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.07,0:07:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and the old man Garp would beat us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.07,0:07:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We were gonna become pirates...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So I forfeited my noble heritage\Nand I planned to carry on living with the two.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.87,0:07:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But one day, my father came\Nand forced me to come back with him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.62,0:07:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave the rest up to you,\Npirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.17,0:07:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, mister.\NYou've already paid us for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.42,0:08:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will take care of these two\Nso they won't bother your boy again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.39,0:08:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute, Bluejam!\NDad, that's enough! I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.89,0:08:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.48,0:08:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it, Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.19,0:08:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do as you say.\NI'll live as you want so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.03,0:08:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...please don't hurt these two!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're very important to \Nme, they're my brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.09,0:08:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.29,0:08:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then go home right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.76,0:08:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should stop playing pirate -\Nit's just a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.85,0:08:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.60,0:08:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.18,0:08:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo, run!\NYou don't have to worry about us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.73,0:08:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you wanna live freely with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.48,0:08:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo, don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.12,0:09:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna put an end to your dream?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.07,0:09:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.70,0:09:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.08,0:09:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.37,0:09:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At that time, all I could do was\Nturn my back and scream in my mind...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.96,0:09:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Spread your wings and \Nfly away freely for me."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.63,0:09:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that you're safe,\Nyoung master.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.80,0:09:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sabo! You're back.\NYou got bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.55,0:09:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.55,0:09:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now Stelly,\Nsay "hi" to your older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.72,0:09:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, brother!\NMy name is Stelly and I'm eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.91,0:09:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fire?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.82,0:09:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You don't know about it\Nbecause you weren't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.11,0:09:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they decided it months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.11,0:09:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They decided to burn down the Gray Terminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.99,0:09:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then this country will be clean!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.72,0:09:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!\NThat's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.50,0:10:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gonna burn up\N{\i1}all{\i0} the shame of this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.30,0:10:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!\NYou have to evacuate!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.72,0:10:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace! Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.30,0:10:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.07,0:10:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to you, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.20,0:10:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This town smells worse \Nthan the Gray Terminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.49,0:10:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It smells like rotten people!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.26,0:10:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I stay here... I'll never be free!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.39,0:10:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.73,0:10:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...ashamed of being born a noble!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.15,0:11:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They finally made a kid say this!\NGoa Kingdom!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.70,0:11:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a nice day!\NIt's perfect for setting sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.66,0:11:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I set off.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.83,0:11:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I left my noble heritage, parents,\Nand country behind...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.54,0:11:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...to live as the freest pirate ever!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.64,0:11:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How rude is that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.83,0:11:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saint Jalmack!\NThere is a child on the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.48,0:11:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When someone flies a black flag,\Nhe's a pirate regardless of who he is-{\i1}eh{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.87,0:11:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But most importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.19,0:11:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A commoner shouldn't cross\Nthe path of my ship!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.14,0:12:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ace... Luffy...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.06,0:12:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Help me... Somebody...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.70,0:12:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I met Dragon-san there\Nand it changed my destiny...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.88,0:12:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the damn Celestial Dragons are up there...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.13,0:13:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ready. Let's do it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.73,0:13:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief of Staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.05,0:13:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.25,0:13:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They sank his ship so you must've \Nthought that Sabo guy was dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.42,0:13:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I thought so at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.18,0:13:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cried a lot when Pedro died.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.35,0:13:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know how you felt!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.28,0:13:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ace... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.52,0:13:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna become stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.36,0:13:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I can protect anything or anyone!\NI don't have to lose anybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.53,0:14:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.00,0:14:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.29,0:14:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,please don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.33,0:14:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.30,0:14:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Worry about yourself first!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.94,0:14:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're far weaker than me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.55,0:14:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.22,0:14:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never die!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.14,0:14:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.81,0:14:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo told me to take care of you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.27,0:14:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise that I'll never die!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.57,0:14:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I leave a wimpy \Nbrother like you behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.53,0:14:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh! Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.82,0:14:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not smart so I don't quite know\Nwhat really killed Sabo yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.62,0:14:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it must be something opposed to freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.25,0:14:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo died before he knew freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.96,0:14:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We exchanged that same cup of {\i1}sake{\i0}\Nand we're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.30,0:14:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So listen, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.05,0:15:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to live without leaving any regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.93,0:15:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.14,0:15:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta go out to sea someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.23,0:15:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and live as we like.\NFreer than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.61,0:15:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.36,0:15:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means we'll make enemies of many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.16,0:15:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the old man will become our enemy.\NYou gotta be willing to risk everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.08,0:15:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go out to sea at 17!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.54,0:15:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we will become... pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.13,0:15:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start with finding a crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.18,0:15:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want at least 10 of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.85,0:15:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the black flag!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.72,0:15:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.85,0:15:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.40,0:15:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.32,0:16:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Sabo-{\i1}san{\i0} and Ace-{\i1}san{\i0} had an \Nimpact on Luffy-{\i1}san{\i0}'s sailing-out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.53,0:16:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that nice?! He sailed out for\Na never-ending adventure!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.66,0:16:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And your brother Sabo \Nwho you thought was dead
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.26,0:16:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is now the No.2 of the Revolutionary Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.17,0:16:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Revolutionary Army's leader\Nis your father, Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.13,0:16:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other brother, Portgas D. Ace
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.64,0:16:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was the Whitebeard Pirates' \N2nd division commander
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.65,0:16:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the King of the Pirates \N- Gol D. Roger's son...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.24,0:16:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of family is that?!\NToo many badasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.44,0:16:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it make you feel strange \Nwhen you think that your sworn
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.13,0:16:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,brother is with your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.11,0:16:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmmm...  I don't know\Nbecause I've never met my dad before...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.45,0:16:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.62,0:16:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,wherever I am,\Nit feels like I'm always connected to Sabo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.44,0:17:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The king of the Goa Kingdom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.50,0:17:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The king of the Goa Kingdom, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.32,0:17:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a peaceful rural kingdom\Nbut it's home to a number of outlaws.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.12,0:17:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garp is an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.83,0:17:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The leader of the Revolutionary Army - Dragon,\Nthe Chief of Staff - Sabo,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.29,0:17:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the pirates - "Fire Fist" and Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.42,0:17:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.84,0:17:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, kneel at my feet, Garp!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.65,0:17:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of my way. Your face irritates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.72,0:17:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His rudeness leaves me speechless!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.52,0:17:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cut to the chase, Garp.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.02,0:17:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me some pull with the World Nobles!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.57,0:17:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna eventually become a Celestial Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.91,0:18:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna be a scumbag like them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.11,0:18:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.25,0:18:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, please! Did anyone hear that?!\NThat could get us the death penalty!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.58,0:18:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I shouldn't say that. I take it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.75,0:18:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He scares me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.63,0:18:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay-{\i1}jamon{\i0}, young man?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.30,0:18:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.36,0:18:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He moved?! I thought he was a building!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.97,0:18:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is he a Giant? I heard they eat humans\Nand can melt rocks with their saliva...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.98,0:18:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, wait. Who are they?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.02,0:18:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fangs?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.86,0:18:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Scales?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.40,0:18:47.12,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Look at the colors of their skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.14,0:18:50.60,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they Fish-Men who are \Nhalf-human and half-fish?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.62,0:18:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're classified as fish and you'll \Nget a rare disease by touching them...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.37,0:19:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.84,0:19:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bondola 2, now departing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.64,0:19:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, take care of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.39,0:19:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-{\i1}sama{\i0}'s grandfather-{\i1}sama{\i0},\Nthank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.52,0:19:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was fun to travel with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.53,0:19:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so high...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.60,0:20:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.69,0:20:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter-{\i1}jamon{\i0}, Shirahoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.70,0:20:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father-{\i1}sama{\i0}... It's the sun...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.99,0:20:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother-{\i1}sama{\i0}! The sun is shining so brightly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.83,0:20:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.04,0:20:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sky goes on forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.42,0:20:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea is also endless\Nand sparkling in the sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.01,0:20:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's really amazing! Mambo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.02,0:20:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know that the \Nsurface was so dazzling!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.23,0:20:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a beautiful world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.07,0:20:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.48,0:20:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sun Tree that lights up the sea floor\Ncan't compare-{\i1}jamon{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.74,0:20:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father-{\i1}sama{\i0}, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.04,0:21:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If possible, I want to live on land!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.78,0:21:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to show this world in the sun\Nto the people of our kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.47,0:21:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask them.\NThat's what the Reverie is all about-{\i1}jamon{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.49,0:21:21.21,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,KAMABAKKA KINGDOM
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.23,0:21:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're fighting against the \NWorld Government for the Fish-Men,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.40,0:21:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,do you have mixed feelings, Koala?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.11,0:21:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About the Ryugu Kingdom \Nattending the Reverie?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.99,0:21:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't, Betty-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.49,0:21:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not the World Government\Nthat we really wanna bring down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.12,0:21:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Celestial Dragons who rule it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.06,0:21:48.86,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,RED LINE
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.88,0:21:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really high! I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.30,0:21:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very windy! And it's shaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.98,0:22:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.85,0:22:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-D-Did you just see that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.80,0:22:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.72,0:22:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a G-Giant in the wall,\Nstaring at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.84,0:22:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-H-He had a trident!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.76,0:22:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be hallucinating...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.79,0:22:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you see how high we're at now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.13,0:22:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was really there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.63,0:22:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Look over there! They're crows!\N--They don't usually come up this high.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.76,0:22:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are the birds that \Neveryone was talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.65,0:22:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.43,0:22:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they peck at the bubble, we're gonna fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.66,0:22:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guard! Pull out your gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.39,0:22:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot down the crows!\NThey're gonna pop the bubble!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.03,0:22:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.60,0:23:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be fine. King Stelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.58,0:23:12.86,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Vivi from Alabasta. Rebecca from Dressrosa.\NAnd Shirahoshi from the Fish-Man Island.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.88,0:23:15.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The three heroines who once stood up
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.43,0:23:18.20,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,to save their countries\Nfrom crises along with the Straw Hats,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.22,0:23:21.83,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}meet each other with memories \Nof Luffy in their mind!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.85,0:23:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"I Miss Him! Vivi and Rebecca's Sentiments!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.35,0:23:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
